  "body": "### Description\n\nplease add support for [istio proxyless grpc](https://istio.io/latest/blog/2021/proxyless-grpc). this will allow grpc client and services to take advantage of all of the istio goodies without having to pay for the proxy performance tax.\r\n\r\nas a developer I'd like to configure the XSD endpoint from which to load the grpc configuration  (either client or server) as a quakus configuration item.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nas far as I can see the base java libra already supports this: https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/doc/grpc_xds_features.md\r\n\r\nso it's a matter of integrating this capabilities at the higher level vertx-grpc and quarkus-grpc.\r\n",
